# Pantone Mug - Pride

## Have coffee with pride!

Sku#: 101030001

$ 30.00

Add To Cart

Enjoy your favorite hot beverage in this colorful mug. The Pride Mug is a vibrant and meaningful way to celebrate diversity and inclusion. This mug features the seven colors symbolizing LGBTQ+ pride and unity. The colorful bands create a striking visual appeal, making it perfect for daily use for your home or office. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or gifting it to a loved one, this mug stands as a bold expression of love, equality, and solidarity.

